# GitHub Ignore for Hardcore Systems Cheatsheet

# Ignore all LaTeX source files
**/*.tex

# Ignore all Python build scripts (protecting the conversion engine)
**/*.py

# Ignore LaTeX compilation temp files
**/*.aux
**/*.log
**/*.out
**/*.toc
**/*.synctex.gz
**/*.fdb_latexmk
**/*.fls
**/*.xdv

# Ignore operating system files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Ensure we track everything in the docs/ folder (compiled outputs for Pages)
!docs/**
